GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
H 1
HOUSE JOINT RESOLUTION 1007
Sponsors: Representative Bell.
For a complete list of sponsors, refer to the North Carolina General Assembly web site.
Referred to: Rules, Calendar, and Operations of the House
April 16, 2025
1 A JOINT RESOLUTION ADJOURNING THE 2025 GENERAL ASSEMBLY TO A DATE
2 CERTAIN.
3 Be it resolved by the House of Representatives, the Senate concurring:
4 SECTION 1. When the House of Representatives and the Senate adjourn on
5 Thursday, April 17, 2025, they stand adjourned to reconvene on Monday, April 28, 2025, at
6 12:00 noon.
7 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon ratification.
